00:31:04,750 --> 00:31:05,960
What? Wait.

566
00:31:06,310 --> 00:31:07,200
Niece-in-law?

567
00:31:07,840 --> 00:31:08,750
How come I didn't know?

568
00:31:08,990 --> 00:31:10,880
It was from Lin'an.

569
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:12,750
Lin'an is the best.

570
00:31:12,750 --> 00:31:15,440
She buys me different yogurts
every day.

571
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:16,750
It's so delicious!

572
00:31:19,750 --> 00:31:20,600
Oh, it's Lin'an.

573
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:22,470
While you were away,

574
00:31:22,470 --> 00:31:25,550
Princess Lin'an would send gifts to us
from time to time.

575
00:31:26,030 --> 00:31:27,230
Princess Lin'an gave Father

576
00:31:27,230 --> 00:31:29,600
the golden saber on him yesterday.

577
00:31:31,310 --> 00:31:32,840
He loves it.

578
00:31:32,840 --> 00:31:35,160
Last night, he was holding it
while sleeping.

579
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,840
He didn't even hold me.

580
00:31:40,210 --> 00:31:42,470
Speaking of Princess Lin'an,
she'd send people every day

581
00:31:42,470 --> 00:31:44,160
to ask when you'd return.

582
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,330
