repeatedly telling me

596
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:39,310
to safely bring you back to the capital,

597
00:32:40,160 --> 00:32:43,200
I'd throw you into the bandit's den
and let you fend for yourself.

598
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:44,710
Anyway, we're entering the city.

599
00:32:45,840 --> 00:32:46,680
After that,

600
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:48,270
I'll make sure to repay you.

601
00:32:57,750 --> 00:32:58,640
Your Highness,

602
00:32:58,640 --> 00:33:00,070
