603
00:33:00,360 --> 00:33:01,540
If Father won't meet with me,

604
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:03,440
I'll kneel here until dawn.

605
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:10,150
Lin'an.

606
00:33:17,030 --> 00:33:17,990
The ground is cold.

607
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:19,400
Come back with me.

608
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:20,240
Be good.

609
00:33:21,470 --> 00:33:22,310
Mother,

610
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,550
