611
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,330
that a gentleman doesn't harm others

612
00:33:26,410 --> 00:33:27,230
or deceive himself.

613
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:29,680
Although I am not talented,

614
00:33:30,270 --> 00:33:32,070
I always remember this.

615
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:35,790
Uncle's massacre has caused uproar

616
00:33:36,120 --> 00:33:37,790
in the city today.

617
00:33:38,310 --> 00:33:39,710
The officials tried to advise,

618
00:33:40,070 --> 00:33:41,710
yet Father avoided them.

619
00:33:42,840 --> 00:33:43,990
As his daughter,

620
00:33:44,990 --> 00:33:46,550
