629
00:34:07,030 --> 00:34:07,870
Mother.

630
00:34:07,880 --> 00:34:08,920
The princess...

631
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:11,720
The princess is concerned
about His Majesty's health,

632
00:34:11,990 --> 00:34:13,670
