- Let's go.

633
00:34:13,700 --> 00:34:15,220
Now, her knees hurt too much to stand.

634
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:15,830
Hurry.

635
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:17,320
Help her back to the Palace to rest.

636
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:23,960
Something serious happened in Chuzhou.

637
00:34:24,240 --> 00:34:25,880
Today, the officials caused uproar.

638
00:34:25,880 --> 00:34:27,720
Everyone's talking about it.

639
00:34:29,440 --> 00:34:30,440
What happened?

640
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:33,590
What's so serious?

641
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:36,510
You're a woman.

642
00:34:36,510 --> 00:34:38,110
Why are you asking so many questions?

643
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:41,670
The Dafeng actually has such a beast.

644
00:34:41,720 --> 00:34:43,240
Let's go inside to play.

645
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:44,880
No wonder.

646
00:34:45,670 --> 00:34:47,990
