713
00:37:31,990 --> 00:37:33,150
Why?

714
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:36,030
The Supervisor held me back!

715
00:37:41,720 --> 00:37:42,670
However,

716
00:37:43,590 --> 00:37:45,590
it wasn't Xu Ningyan

717
00:37:45,670 --> 00:37:47,360
