718
00:37:47,720 --> 00:37:50,030
I feel much better.

719
00:37:50,190 --> 00:37:51,070
That kid

720
00:37:51,070 --> 00:37:52,110
took my chance away.

721
00:37:52,110 --> 00:37:52,960
